    public static final class Chaincode.ChaincodeData.Builder
extends com.google.protobuf.GeneratedMessageV3.Builder<Chaincode.ChaincodeData.Builder>
implements Chaincode.ChaincodeDataOrBuilder
     ChaincodeData defines the datastructure for chaincodes to be serialized by proto
 Type provides an additional check by directing to use a specific package after instantiation
 Data is Type specific (see CDSPackage and SignedCDSPackage)
